Key Match Events: Kuwait and India played a scoreless draw in the FIFA World Cup 2026 qualifiers at Salt Lake Stadium in Kolkata.
The encounter was part of the fifth round of Group A.
This was Sunil Chhetri’s final game in international colors.
Post-Match Reflections: The goalless draw was not the fitting finale India would have wanted for Chhetri.
India’s hopes of advancing to the third round of the FIFA World Cup Qualifiers look slim as they face a tough test against Qatar in their final match of the second round.
